              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="grid_4">
              <a href="#" class="video_image_button image_preview">
                <span class="play">Play Video</span>
                <img src="images/video_previews/3_capture.jpg" alt="" />
              </a>
              <a href="#" class="video_image_button title">Video and Image capture</a>
              <p>
                Learn how easy it is to capture images from your computer screen, resize and capture them. Capture a video and embed it just by playing it on your computer.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="line">
          
            <div class="grid_4">
              <a href="#" class="autotext_button image_preview">
                <span class="play">Play Video</span>
